PEOPLE
v.
PINON. No. S229632. Supreme Court of California July 27, 2016. CANTIL-SAKAUYE, C.J., WERDEGAR, CHIN, CORRIGAN, LIU, CUÉLLAR, and KRUGER, JJ., concur.

The above entitled matter is transferred to the Court of Appeal, Fourth Appellate District, Division Three, with directions to vacate its decision and to reconsider the cause in light of People v. Morales (2016) 63 Cal.4th 399 , 203 Cal.Rptr.3d 130 , 371 P.3d 592 . (Cal. Rules of Court, rule 8.528(d).)
